'''''The Michelle Obama Musiaqualogy''''' is an American music collection curated by [[Questlove]] which serves as a soundtrack to [[Michelle Obama]]'s 2018 book ''[[Becoming (book)|Becoming]]''. The collection has 300 tracks and includes music by [[Michael Jackson]], [[Prince (musician)|Prince]], [[Kendrick Lamar]], [[Beyoncé]], [[Erykah Badu]], [[Aretha Franklin]] and others. The soundtrack is divided into three parts, the first playlist spanning from 1964 to 1979, the second playlist spanning from 1980 to 1997, and the third playlist spanning from 1997 to 2018.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/8486074/questlove-michelle-obama-become-book-tour-soundtrack-stream|title=Questlove Expertly Curates Soundtrack for Michelle Obama's 'Becoming' Book Tour: Listen|last=Stutz|first=Colin|date=November 20, 2018|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|access-date=November 21, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://pitchfork.com/news/questlove-curated-michelle-obamas-book-tour-soundtrack-listen/|title=Questlove Curated Michelle Obama’s Book Tour Soundtrack: Listen|last=Blais-Billie|first=Braudie|date=November 20, 2018|work=[[Pitchfork (website)|Pitchfork]]|access-date=November 21, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.spin.com/2018/11/michelle-obama-questlove-book-tour-playlist/|title=Listen to Questlove’s Curated Soundtrack for Michelle Obama’s Book Tour|last=Burks|first=Tosten|date=November 20, 2018|work=[[Spin (magazine)|Spin]]|access-date=November 21, 2018}}</ref>

